{
  "bio": [
    "Vasily Anisimov is a Russian-born billionaire who made his first fortune in non-ferrous metals trading.",
    "Later he became a partner of billionaires Alisher Usmanov and Andrei Skoch, before selling out to move into real estate. He also has interests in African uranium mining.",
    "Anisimov was a head of the Russian Judo Federation for 12 years, until October 2022; its first vice president is Putin's friend Arkady Rotenberg.",
    "He renounced his Russian citizenship in 2022 and now holds a Croatian passport."
  ],
  "about": [
    "The 2024 Oligarch-themed Romantic Comedy, \"Anora\", was filmed in Anisimov's former mansion in Brooklyn, NY."
